            ("ENGAGEMENT SERVICES", "This letter confirms the arrangements regarding the services CyberCompliance Inc. (\"Provider\") is to perform for ClearLedger, LLC (the \"Company\") related to its Sales Tax Service system (the \"Service Organization's System\"). Provider will perform an examination of the Service Organization's System in accordance with attestation standards established by the American Institute of Certified Public Accountants (\"AICPA\"), and in relation to the criteria stated in management's assertion. Provider will plan and perform such procedures as necessary to obtain reasonable assurance about whether management's description of the Service Organization's System fairly presents the system that was designed and implemented for the period October 1, 2024, to September 30, 2025.\n\nThe Company uses subservice organizations for tax payment processing and hosting services. Management's description includes the services provided by the subservice organizations, but the control objectives and related controls of those subservice organizations are not included in the scope of this engagement. At the conclusion of the examination, Provider will issue a written SOC 1, Type 2 report addressed to the management of the Company."),
